---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About — Yannik Peschke" 
  description="Learn more about Yannik Peschke, Software Architect specializing in micro-frontend architectures and the Rspack ecosystem."
>

<h1>About Me</h1>

  <p>
    I'm a Software Architect focused on building complex, scalable and distributed web ecosystems. 
    My work centers on creating and orchestrating interconnected frontend architectures, maintainable codebases and custom tooling for teams to accelerate.

  <p>
    I strongly believe in sharing knowledge and learning in public.
  </p>
  <p>
    I help teams move fast and independently using Module Federation and the evolving Rspack ecosystem—where I actively contribute and advocate.
  </p>
  <p>
    When I started my coding journey, jQuery was still the GOAT, and I still value pragmatic problem-solving over hype.
  </p>
  <p>
    Arch Linux, Neovim, Open Source Software and building systems that don’t fight their users are my happy place.
  </p>

<p>
Outside of work, I love running mountain trails, reading a good book, or cooking for family and friends. I’m endlessly curious and always looking for new ways to learn and grow.
</p>

<h2>Work & Expertise</h2>

<p>
As a Software Architect, I focus on transforming highly complex monolithic web systems into dynamic, interconnected micro-frontend architectures. I lead the technical orchestration of frontends, enabling decentralized teams to collaborate efficiently across a shared customer journey.

My north star is delivering products that are performant, secure, resilient, and seamless. Beyond architecture, I own onboarding and governance practices and documentations and act as a technical mentor and consultant for developers, stakeholders, and design teams.
</p>

<p>
  When I code outside of work, it’s usually exploratory—researching ideas or refining my Neovim setup. I’m intentional about maintaining balance between work and personal time. Active recovery and focus are important to consistently deliver high-quality outcomes at work.
</p>

<div class="contact-section">
  <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>
  I'm always interested in connecting with other engineers or people from the tech-bubble. It is important to stay open-minded and discuss on tech-trends, complex architecture problems or just enjoying the Open Source Community. - Ping me and let's have a chat.
  </p>
  <div class="contact-links">
    <a href="https://github.com/YanPes" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yannik-peschke-a48012108/" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
    <a href="https://x.com/_yanpes" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a>
  </div>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
/* Single body text size for consistent hierarchy */
p,
.skill-list,
.tool-list,
.tool-list li {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
}

.intro {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
}

.experience-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
}

.experience-item {
  padding-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.experience-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.experience-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--spacing-xs);
}

.experience-title {
  font-family: var(--font-main);
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.experience-period {
  font-family: var(--font-main);
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.experience-description {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.skills-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
}

.skill-category {
  padding: var(--spacing-md);
  padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
  background-color: transparent;
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  position: relative;
}

.skill-category:hover {
  border-left-color: var(--accent);
  padding-left: calc(var(--spacing-lg) + 10px);
}

.skill-category h3 {
  margin-top: 0;
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.skill-category h3::before {
  content: ">";
  margin-right: 10px;
  color: var(--accent);
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateX(-10px);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.skill-category:hover h3::before {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateX(0);
}

.skill-list {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
}

.skill-list:last-of-type {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.balance-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.balance-list li {
  padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.balance-list li:hover {
  color: var(--text-primary);
  transform: translateX(5px);
}

.balance-list li::before {
  content: "*";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  font-family: var(--font-main);
}

.balance-list li:hover::before {
  color: var(--accent);
}

.tool-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm) 0;
}

.tool-list li {
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.tool-list li:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.tool-list strong {
  color: var(--text-primary);
}

.contact-section {
  margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.contact-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
}

.contact-link {
  font-family: var(--font-main);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.contact-link:hover {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--accent);
  border-color: var(--accent);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(192, 254, 4, 0.2);
}

h2:first-of-type {
  margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .skills-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .experience-header {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
</style>
